      • getArticle

        public void getArticle(java.lang.String fileName,
              int timeout)
                throws JPARSECException
        Obtains the article for this bibtex object. If the article requires subscription, no file will be created.
        Parameters:
        fileName - Name of the .pdf file to create.
        timeout - Timeout in milliseconds. If the connection waits for data for more than this time an exception will be thrown.
        Throws:
        JPARSECException - If an error occurs, for example if no full .pdf article is available.
